    ('Applied Linguistics','Are you interested in how children acquire language, how the skills of second-language speakers develop, how various language disorders can be diagnosed and treated, or how social or cultural environments interact with language?','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/applied-linguistics/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Biochemistry','At Brock, our teaching and research labs are combined. This means you.9ll apply current techniques and technology to biochemical problems using the same state-of-the-art equipment that our professors use for their research.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/chemistry/','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.70%).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), or second 4U math or English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Biological Sciences','We are ranked highly among undergraduate Canadian universities in medical and science research grants. You.9ll have access to modern labs and the teaching and research knowledge of professors who have received provincial, national and international acclaim for their work.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/biology/','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.70%).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), or second 4U math or English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Biomedical Sciences','This exciting program is intended for those interested in a career in medicine or biomedical research. The program is offered jointly by the Departments of Biological Sciences and Health Sciences and is focused on the molecular basis of human health.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/biology/','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.70%).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), or second 4U math or English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Biophysics','Biophysics is the physics of life, of all living systems and their interaction with their surroundings, both natural and artificial. It is a rapidly advancing field, encompassing a wide variety of areas in natural and life sciences.','http://www.physics.brocku.ca/','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.70%).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), or second 4U math or English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Biotechnology','You.9ll be on the forefront of research in this exciting and knowledge-based industry. You.9ll take courses in biological sciences, chemistry, biochemistry and biotechnology, exploring the use of living organisms to produce goods and services for practical and industrial purposes.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/biotechnology','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.70%).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), or second 4U math or English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Business Administration','Our Bachelor of Business Administration (BBA) program combines professionally oriented business courses with studies in social sciences, humanities and mathematics and science.','https://brocku.ca/goodman/programs/bba/','English (ENG4U).Two 4U maths','Goodman School of Business'),
    ('Business Administration Co-op International Double Degree','We.9ve partnered with five leading business schools in Europe to offer you the best in global business education.','https://brocku.ca/goodman/programs/international-dual-degree/','English (ENG4U).Two 4U maths','Goodman School of Business'),
    ('Business Communication','This program aims to equip students with a sound theoretical basis for analyzing and practicing communication within the business environment.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/cpcf/','English (ENG 4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Business Economics','Our Bachelor of Business Economics program is unique in Canada. If you.9re interested in combining the studies of economics and business, this degree offers you the best opportunity.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/economics/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min. 65%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min. 65%)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Canadian Studies','Canadian Studies is offered as a combined major. As a Canadian Studies co-major, you.9ll confront the intersection of Canada.9s rich history with culture, cultural policy, politics, economics and geography.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/canadian-studies','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Chemistry','We have some of the most advanced equipment in the field. While other schools often reserve the newest equipment exclusively for research, all of Brock.9s facilities are used for both teaching and research.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/chemistry/','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.70%).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), or second 4U math or English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Child Health','This unique four-year program is for individuals who aspire to develop a career working with children in a health-related profession.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/health-sciences/','English (ENG4U).Biology (SBI4U)','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Computer Science','We.9ll prepare you for a career in Information Technology (IT), an industry that is transforming our world and workplaces. You.9ll study data structures, operating systems, database systems, industry-standard programming languages, software engineering and user interfaces.','http://www.cosc.brocku.ca/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Community Health','This program is ideal for students who are interested in acquiring a well-rounded understanding of health and wellness at the individual and societal levels.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/health-sciences/','English (ENG4U).One of Biology (SB14U) or Chemistry (SCH4U)','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Computing and Business','Our program provides a unique foundation in business practices for computing professionals. The program begins with core courses in computer programming, basic data structures and computer organization, augmented by courses in accounting, management and economics.','http://www.cosc.brocku.ca/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U).A second 4U math (min. 75% between two math)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Concurrent Teacher Education .3 Intermediate/Senior (Grades 7-12)','These programs focus on grades seven to twelve, with an emphasis on secondary school.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/','All majors - English (ENG4U), one 4U math.French Studies majors only - One of FSF4U, FEF4U or FIF4U.Dramatic Arts majors only - Attendance at DART Invitational mandatory.Visual Arts majors only - Submission of Visual Arts portfolio mandatory','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Computing and Network Communications','We.9ve teamed up with the School of Applied Computing and Engineering Sciences at Sheridan College to develop a program where you may complete your Brock degree and a three-year diploma in Telecommunications Technology from Sheridan College in just 4.5 years.','http://www.cosc.brocku.ca/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min. 70%)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Concurrent Teacher Education .3 Primary/Junior (Grades K-6)','You.9ll study for six years to complete an Honours BA in Child and Youth Studies and a Bachelor of Education (BEd) at the same time.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/','English (ENG4U).One 4U math (Mathematics of Data Management - MDM4U preferred).Students admitted directly from secondary school..For teaching at the Primary-Junior level (Grades K-6).','Faculty of Education'),
    ('Concurrent Teacher Education .3 Junior/Intermediate (Grades 4-10)','These programs focus on grades four to ten, with an emphasis on elementary school.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/','English (ENG4U).One 4U math','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Critical Criminology','The Honours Critical Criminology degree provides students the opportunity for an extensive examination of whose interests are served by .8law and order.9 ideologies, policies and practices of social control.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/programs/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Earth Sciences','The Earth Sciences program trains geoscientists .4 scientists who study the Earth and other planets in order to better understand their origin and history.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/earth-sciences/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), Chemistry (SCH4U), or second 4U math','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Economics','Study the .cscience of choice.d .4 learning how limited resources can best be used to meet the needs of individuals and society. You.9ll look at how individual consumers choose to spend their time and money, and how producers predict and respond to consumer needs.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/economics/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.65%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min. 65%)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Early Childhood Education','Students may build on a two-year ECE diploma or equivalent by completing our focused two-and-a-half year program.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/','Graduate of a two-year Early Childhood Education Diploma program or equivalent with an overall 75% average.','Faculty of Education'),
    ('Dramatic Arts','As a Dramatic Arts (DART) student, you.9ll work with the very best faculty, artists and theatre professionals from Niagara, the GTA and beyond.','https://brocku.ca/miwsfpa/dramatic-arts/','English (ENG4U).Attendance at DART Invitational mandatory.','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Environmental Geoscience','Environmental geoscientists apply their unique understanding of the Earth.9s composition, structure and physical processes to protect the environment and predict geologic and hydrologic hazards.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/earth-sciences/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), Chemistry (SCH4U), or second 4U math','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Environmental Sustainability','Environmental Sustainability seeks to protect the natural environment and ecological health while maintaining or improving the quality of human life.','https://brocku.ca/esrc/minor-in-sustainability/',NULL,'Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('English Language and Literature','Our programs combine academic study with unique practical experience in critical thinking and writing. Courses explore literature from Britain, the United States and Canada, as well as works written in English from all over the world.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/english-language-and-literature/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Engineering Science','Add this minor to any program of study at Brock. We believe Engineering is about making life better for everyone and protecting the environment for generations to come.','https://brocku.ca/math-science',NULL,'Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('French Studies','We offer courses in French language, translation and linguistics, as well as courses on literature from French-speaking countries around the world.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/departments-and-centres/modern-languages/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Game Design','Video games are an increasingly important part of contemporary life and entertainment, and Brock.9s GAME program prepares students to lead and collaborate in the creation of games.','https://brocku.ca/game/','English (ENG4U).A Statement of Interest is mandatory (see brocku.ca/game).','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Forensic Psychology and Criminal Justice','This program takes a career-focused and multi-faceted approach to criminal behaviour, law and the criminal justice system.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/fpac/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Film Studies','Brock has the oldest .4 and one of the most distinguished .4 film studies programs in Canada. The program focuses on critical and historical courses that examine a variety of approaches to film and related media.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/cpcf/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Geography','Study Geography in Niagara .3 one of the world.9s most diverse social and natural landscapes.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/geography/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('German','The Minor in German offers courses from beginner to advanced levels, in which students develop comprehension and writing skills, as well as practice the spoken language.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/departments-and-centres/modern-languages/',NULL,'Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('General Humanities','Our BA in General Humanities is designed to allow you to pursue a more flexible selection of courses, with broad exposure to courses from across all of our Faculties.','https://brocku.ca/humanities','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Game Programming','Video games are an increasingly important part of contemporary life and entertainment. The GAME program prepares students to share and even lead in the creation of games .4 from the programming that makes a game work, to the design and realization of dynamic experiences, and the planning and management of production processes.','https://brocku.ca/game/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min. 70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min. 70%).A Statement of Interest is mandatory (see brocku.ca/game).','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Indigenous Education','The Tecumseh Centre for Aboriginal Research and Education offers several options for those interested in working in an indigenous teaching environment.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/',NULL,'Faculty of Education'),
    ('Interactive Arts and Science','Explore the world of interactive media, games and new models of content creation and delivery.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/digital-humanities/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('History','History is at the heart of every educated citizen. To understand the present and prepare for the future, one must learn about the past.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/history','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Hispanic and Latin American Studies','This program is offered as a combined major. It offers a strong focus on Spanish- and Portuguese-speaking cultures. Spanish and Portuguese have become very popular language choices and are increasingly in demand in today.9s global economy.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/departments-and-centres/modern-languages/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Kinesiology .3 Accelerate Into Master.9s','This one-of-a-kind program in Canada is designed for students wanting to work in kinesiology and related healthcare professions. Students applying to this program from high school will gain entry to both the four-year undergraduate Bachelor of Kinesiology (BKin) degree and the one-year Master of Professional Kinesiology (MPK) program at Brock University.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/kinesiology/','English (ENG4U).Biology (SB14U).One 4U math (MHF4U preferred)','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Labour Studies','Work defines so much of our lives .4 our position in society, our economic well-being, even our self-image.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/labour-studies/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Italian Studies','This program is offered as a combined major. Develop written and spoken competence in Italian and discover the rich and vast world of Italian culture.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/departments-and-centres/modern-languages/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Medieval and Renaissance Studies','This program is offered as a combined major. The focus is on the period from Late Antiquity to the 17th century.','https://brocku.ca/mars','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Media and Communication Studies','Are you interested in studying how people communicate, ways that social structures affect communication, or how new technologies are changing human communications?','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/cpcf/','English (ENG 4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Mathematics and Statistics','This exciting mathematics program is flexible, innovative and provides opportunities for students to work with leading researchers to gain academic and employment experience.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/mathematics/','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min. 75%).Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min. 75%)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Nursing','The Department of Nursing offers an Honours Bachelor of Science in Nursing degree.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/nursing/','English (ENG4U) (min.75%).Biology (SBI4U) (min.75%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.75%).One 4U Math (min.75%)','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Oenology and Viticulture','We.9ll provide you with a comprehensive education encompassing sensory science, biochemistry, biotechnology, chemistry, microbiology, genetics, molecular biology, plant physiology and cell biology.','https://brocku.ca/ccovi/graduate-undergraduate-studies/','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.70%).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), or second 4U math or English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Neuroscience','Neuroscience is the study of the nervous system and how it generates behaviour in animals and humans.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/neuroscience/','Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min.70%).Chemistry (SCH4U) (min.70%).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), or second 4U math or English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Music','The Department of Music trains our students to become critically aware musicians and prepares you for your chosen musical career by laying a foundation in performance, theory and musicianship.','https://brocku.ca/miwsfpa/music/','English (ENG4U).A theory placement test (RMC advanced Rudiments) and aural skills test must be passed..Entrance evaluation required - see the department website for details.','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Political Science','Our program looks at five key areas.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/political-science/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Physical Education','Brock.9s Physical Education program is the Faculty.9s longest-standing program and offers outstanding potential for those interested in physical literacy, human movement, performance and inclusive physical activity education.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/kinesiology/','English (ENG4U).Biology (SBI4U).One 4U math','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Philosophy','Philosophy, defined as the pursuit of wisdom, encompasses the exploration of the nature of reality, consciousness, values, knowledge, reason, argument and evidence.','https://brocku.ca/humanities/philosophy/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Public Health','As the oldest Bachelor of Public Health degree in Canada, our program provides students with a highly sought-after specialization.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/health-sciences/','English (ENG4U).One of Biology (SBI4U) or Chemistry (SCH4U)','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Public Health .3 Accelerate Into Master.9s','This dual degree program in public health is the first of its kind in Canada. Furthermore, the BPH degree is the oldest in Canada. This highly desirable public health specialization places an emphasis on disease prevention, health policy, promotion and administration as well as evidence-based program analytics.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/health-sciences/','English (ENG4U).One of Biology (SBI4U) or Chemistry (SCH4U)','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Psychology','Psychology is the scientific study of human behaviour, and the program at Brock offers a diverse approach to this exciting field of study.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/departments-and-centres/psychology/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Popular Culture','This program explores issues in popular culture from a multidisciplinary perspective. You.9ll take a series of critical and historical courses examining a wide range of mass-mediated and non mass-mediated forms of popular culture.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/cpcf/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Social Sciences','Our BA in Social Sciences degree is designed to allow you to pursue a more flexible pattern of study than a single or combined major.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Sociology','Sociology as a discipline challenges everyday assumptions about the world in which we live. Sociologists turn .8common sense.9 ideas on their head through critical examination of social institutions, relationships and conditions shaping the world and the experiences of individuals.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/sociology/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Sciences','Create a custom program for yourself. This program has been designed for individuals wishing to acquire the knowledge and skills necessary to pursue further undergraduate and graduate studies, or careers in the sciences in a personalized and flexible way.','https://brocku.ca/math-science','Two from: SB14U (Biology), SC4U (Chemistry), SPH4U (Physics), MCV4U (Calculus and Vectors), MHF4U (Functions), SES4U (Earth and Space Science), ICS4U (Computer Studies)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Recreation and Leisure Studies','Recreation professionals deliver health, social, economic and environmental benefits through leisure services.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/recreation-leisure/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Teacher Education .3 Consecutive','This program is for those who have already completed a university degree. The program is four semesters, taken over two academic years, allowing students time to learn, reflect and grow as beginning teachers.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/','University Degree','Faculty of Education'),
    ('Technological Education','This program is for those with professional qualifications in a broad-based technology, several years of relevant work experience and a passion to teach secondary students.','https://brocku.ca/education',NULL,'Faculty of Education'),
    ('Studies in Arts and Culture','The Studies in Arts and Culture (STAC) program welcomes students who wish to explore and gain a critical view of contemporary culture by engaging in pragmatic and experiential learning.','https://brocku.ca/miwsfpa/stac/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Sport Management','Brock is the only university in Canada granting a specialized Bachelor of Sport Management (BSM) degree. Our program has an outstanding reputation within the sport industry for the quality of our students and graduates.','https://brocku.ca/applied-health-sciences/sport-management/','English (ENG4U).One 4U mathematics','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Visual Arts','In the Department of Visual Arts (VISA), education takes place within well-equipped studios and teaching spaces, as well as in our vibrant local arts community. We provide education in two distinct but interconnected streams: Studio Art (STDA) and the History of Art and Visual Culture (HAVC).','https://brocku.ca/miwsfpa/visual-arts','English (ENG4U).Submission of Visual Arts portfolio mandatory (Studio Arts majors only)','Faculty of Humanities'),
    ('Women.9s and Gender Studies','You.9ll examine how social constructions of gender shape the consciousness and lives of women and men of various races, ethnicities, classes and sexualities. You.9ll explore diverse women.9s histories, intellectual contributions and perspectives.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/womens-studies/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
    ('Tourism Studies','Study tourism in Niagara .4 one of the world.9s premier travel destinations and home to a UNESCO Biosphere Reserve.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/geography/','English (ENG4U)','Faculty of Social Sciences');


